            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "彭博新聞午間分享 你會想知道的五件事",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">搭建橋梁</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博創新經濟論壇在新加坡開幕。今年論壇的主題是：在極端時代中蓬勃發展。彭博有限合夥企業創始人兼大股東邁克爾·布隆伯格在發表開幕致辭時表示，論壇旨在搭建橋梁，尤其是在分化加劇的當下。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中日爭端</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本首相高市早苗涉台言論引發中日兩國爭端後，雙方緊張關係仍在持續。據媒體報導，中國外交部亞洲司司長劉勁松表示，他對與日本外務省亞大局局長金井正彰的磋商結果「不滿意」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">需求湧现</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國自9月底向各類境外投資者開放在岸債券回購市場，債券通用戶利用持倉人民幣債券進行融資的需求已經開始湧现。根據中債登(ChinaBond)周一尾盤公佈的數據，境外機構10月份買斷式回購交易結算量為240.56億元人民幣，較9月增加兩成，增量主要來自於「債券通」渠道。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-478337b9-8fe0-3551-b67b-dea1349f97a2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">基金動向</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管全球資金大量湧入人工智能領域，但Orbis新興市場股票基金的Stefan Magnusson不為所動。這位駐香港的基金經理以基本面為選股依據，偏愛那些他認為運營穩健、值得多年持有的公司，今年以來該基金已實現54%的收益。此外，量化投資公司Y-Intercept (Hong Kong) Ltd.據悉已為一支對沖基金籌集超過17億美元，這是近年來亞洲最成功的對沖基金融資活動之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">言歸於好</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">埃隆·馬斯克周二返回白宮，顯示美國總統唐納德·川普與這位世界首富之間的緊張關係已經解凍。馬斯克受邀出席了為沙烏地王儲穆罕默德·本·薩勒曼舉辦的盛大晚宴。其他受邀的眾多商業巨頭還有蒂姆·庫克、大衛·埃利森、馬克·貝尼奧夫、比爾·阿克曼和黃仁勳等。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%8D%88%E9%96%93%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E6%83%B3%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B-041503568.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-19 12:50:47",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英國通膨率七個月來首次下降 英國央行降息押注升溫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/a4FiYer2K3f.0yF4JQApDQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a6ca58ac9193e0d548d3401cad6becfd\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 英國央行考慮是否要在聖誕節前降息之際，英國通膨率七個月來首次下降，表明物價壓力已過峰值。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國國家統計局周三公佈，10月消費者價格指數(CPI)同比上漲3.6%，漲幅低於9月的3.8%。這一數字略高於倫敦金融城經濟學家預測的3.5%，但與英國央行的預測相符。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"632\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/quSmDfco1by0hJS37ALqdw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9b95a61d056d0ecd8feac51bb4e1219e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">受能源價格漲幅低於上年同期影響，通膨率降至6月以來的最低水平。受到英國央行密切關注的服務業通膨率小幅回落至4.5%，低於該行預期。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8c2fcb46-6391-3221-8182-d55fddc0cc14-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述數據令市場對英國央行在聖誕節前的下一次會議上降息的預期得以維持，該行在本月早些時候的會議上按兵不動。英鎊兌美元抹去稍早漲幅，跌0.1%至1.3134。交易員加大押注英國央行將放鬆貨幣政策，市場預期下月降息概率達80%，料明年年底前將累計降息63個基點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「通膨見頂的跡象應該會促使天平向12月降息傾斜，」 Schroders高級經濟學家George Brown表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題UK Inflation Dips for First Time in Seven Months Ahead of Budget</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Joel Rinneby、Harumi Ichikura、Mark Evans.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%83%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8%E5%8D%87%E6%BA%AB-081446214.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-19 17:15:55",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國10年期國債殖利率或將首次低於同期限日債 利差已收窄至歷史最小",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/E61362_rV7dPtaRIYQUPGQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c16340d0a8f00ce1b14e0b9d80aa6f47\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國基準國債殖利率勢將跌到比日債更低的水平，這一歷史性的交叉可能會重新引發人們對中國經濟滑入通縮螺旋的擔憂，而通縮曾讓日本經濟在1990年代深陷困境。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國10年期國債殖利率徘徊在兩個多月最低水平附近，表現乏力的經濟數據以及股市下跌促使投資者尋求國債來避險。另一邊，由於擔心日本政府的支出計畫將加劇通膨，並加重本已沉重的債務負擔，同期限日債殖利率已飆升至2008年以來的最高水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這種相反的殖利率趨勢暗示經濟走勢的轉變：投資者目前預期中國經濟可能出現類似日本過去長期停滯的局面，而東京則終於擺脫數十年的通縮。這也凸顯出在北京重振國內消費的能力方面，市場的信心減弱，而與美國的貿易緊張局勢令出口引擎承壓。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-457493ef-2a1d-3515-ae13-62328ab122ab-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UeOvjFwMqbgz.WKWaaDlYQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b1337128526ca51eb42aa5f72487026c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">債券市場已在反映這種變化，中國10年期國債殖利率為1.81%，日本10年期國債殖利率處於1.77%，殖利率差已縮小至歷史最低水平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：[深度] 什麼是「日本化」？中國在往這條路上走嗎？</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管目前利差是歷史最窄水平，但這主要是由於日本國債殖利率飆升所推動，而非中國殖利率大幅下降所致。不過，這一趨勢仍有可能重塑對這兩個亞洲經濟體的投資格局。轉變已初見端倪，今年第二季度海外投資者持有的日本國債已增至2022年以來最高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「基本經濟趨勢表明，日本的殖利率將上升，而中國的殖利率將下降，」SMBC Nikko Securities的一位高級利率策略師Miki Den表示。「隨著日本10年期國債殖利率將超過中國，我預計未來從中國轉向流入日本的資金將會增加。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’s Key Bond Yield Set to Drop Below Japan’s for First Time</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B10%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%9F%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5%E6%AE%96%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E6%88%96%E5%B0%87%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E4%BD%8E%E6%96%BC%E5%90%8C%E6%9C%9F%E9%99%90%E6%97%A5%E5%82%B5-%E5%88%A9%E5%B7%AE%E5%B7%B2%E6%94%B6%E7%AA%84%E8%87%B3%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%8F-032221663.html",
